"I said, n--he, get out of my property!"
Rascona responds to the fire.
There's a break.
And then everyone (at least all black actors) breaks out in laughter.
Greene laughs the loudest.
"What?!" asked Rascona.
He is alarmed and confused.
Was I too hard?
"No," said Greene, still giggling.
"I just don't think white people said a --- he."
“Yes,” one of the other black actors joked.
